      person("César", "Sánchez-Sellero",
             role = "aut")
    )
Description: Provides prediction intervals for classical (homoscedastic) 
    autoregressive models (AR(p)) and quantile autoregressive models (QAR(p)). 
    The package implements both percentile-based and predictive-root-based 
    bootstrap procedures for multi-step-ahead prediction interval construction.
